h2. Requirements
Battery Shelter MUST be waterproof and SHALL provide insight to the LEDs and access to the Power Button OR MUST be accessible quickly and easily under all conditions, including storm.
Position SHALL be as low as possible.
Position SHALL be as central (referencing boat’s total center of gravity) as possible. Compansating with other loads is an option.
h2. Options
either in standing position like now (no new cable needed)
or laying flat on each hull, in front of the deck house (requires more building and more wiring all along the boat)
h2. Favourite Solution
Build shelter under helm benches (photos attached).
